like, a gallon of blood.

04:19.560 --> 04:21.828
Well, what a charming story.

04:22.896 --> 04:23.797
Oh, so, Lindsay,

04:23.830 --> 04:25.866
have you seen
Ordinary People yet?

04:25.899 --> 04:27.333
No, I haven't seen it.

04:27.367 --> 04:28.569
Oh, well, you have to.

04:29.570 --> 04:30.971
