an Atari for his birthday.

05:16.449 --> 05:18.251
Oh, I asked for it.

05:18.284 --> 05:20.386
That doesn't mean
I'm gonna get it.

05:20.420 --> 05:21.487
LINDSAY:
I'm out of here.

05:21.522 --> 05:22.989
Whoa, wait a minute, there.

05:23.023 --> 05:24.157
Where are you going?

05:24.190 --> 05:25.792
I'm going to the library.

05:25.826 --> 05:28.361
I have to do
some research for
this history paper.

05:28.394 --> 05:29.963
It's on the Panama canal.

05:29.996 --> 05:32.933
Well, could you finish
your dinner first, please?

05:39.372 --> 05:40.406
See ya.

05:40.440 --> 05:42.042
Bye, Linds.

05:47.013 --> 05:48.615
Don't even try it.

05:52.986 --> 05:55.355
Hey, sorry I'm so late.

05:55.388 --> 05:56.557
