dinner reservations.

05:59.092 --> 06:01.695
Can you ever
not be sarcastic?

06:01.728 --> 06:03.229
I'm sarcastic?

06:03.263 --> 06:05.331
DANIEL: All right,
Andopolis, come on.

06:05.365 --> 06:06.900
I'm getting some more fries.

06:08.134 --> 06:09.503
Hey.
Hey.

06:20.280 --> 06:22.583
