want him back.

06:52.613 --> 06:55.248
All right. Yeah, sure.

06:55.281 --> 06:57.450
Look, just don't
lead him on, okay?

06:57.483 --> 06:59.285
'Cause he's obviously
still in love with you.

06:59.319 --> 07:00.787
