07:00.821 --> 07:03.256
Nick is the one who broke up
with me, remember?

07:03.289 --> 07:04.324
Oh, yeah, Lindsay,

07:04.357 --> 07:06.827
like that fooled anybody?
Come on.

07:07.761 --> 07:09.362
Look...

07:09.395 --> 07:12.533
You're just too nice,
you know?

07:12.566 --> 07:14.267
