the wrong idea.

07:14.300 --> 07:17.003
Well, what am I
supposed to be, mean?

07:17.037 --> 07:18.939
No, don't be mean.

07:18.972 --> 07:20.473
Just be a bitch.

07:21.942 --> 07:23.009
I don't know.

07:23.043 --> 07:24.077
Look,

07:24.110 --> 07:26.046
this is for his own good.

07:26.079 --> 07:27.213
Believe me, if he knew

07:27.247 --> 07:28.782
what you were doing,
he'd thank you.

07:28.815 --> 07:30.984
I can't help it,
man, I'm just...

07:31.017 --> 07:32.385
I'm so in love
with her.

07:32.418 --> 07:34.721
Right.
No kidding.

07:34.755 --> 07:37.958
Look, you gotta stop being
so nice to her, all right?

07:37.991 --> 07:39.660
That's how you blew it
the first time.

07:39.693 --> 07:41.227
Oh, like you're the expert,
or something?

07:41.261 --> 07:43.163
