fight all the time.

07:43.196 --> 07:45.999
Yeah, but check
my new strategy.

07:46.032 --> 07:50.103
See, she can flap her lips
all she wants,

07:50.136 --> 07:51.838
I ain't fighting back.

07:51.872 --> 07:55.208
