she runs out of gas.

07:55.241 --> 07:57.310
That is a brilliant plan.

07:57.343 --> 07:58.812
Only took you two years
to figure that out?

07:58.845 --> 08:00.647
It's like the tortoise
and the hare, all right?

08:00.681 --> 08:03.183
Little rabbit
gets tired,

08:03.216 --> 08:04.551
guess who wins?

08:06.653 --> 08:08.488
