the cold shoulder.

08:14.327 --> 08:15.596
I don't...
I don't know, man.

08:15.629 --> 08:17.831
That doesn't seem right.

08:17.864 --> 08:19.633
Trust me.

08:19.666 --> 08:21.367
Don't call her house,

08:21.401 --> 08:23.136
don't write her notes,

08:23.169 --> 08:24.470
